# Basic Calculator

A simple calculator built with **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript** to perform basic arithmetic operations.

## Features
- Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division
- Clear button to reset calculations
- Easy-to-use interface

## How to Use
1. Click the buttons to input numbers and select operations.
2. Press `=` to get the result.
3. Use `C` to clear the display.

## Live Preview
Check out the project here: [Calculator](https://github.com/mubashira22/Calculator)

